{"id":"apharsachites","term":"Apharsachites","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>A company of the colonists whom the Assyrian king planted in Samaria (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 5:6\">Ezra 5:6</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 6:6\">6:6</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Ezra 5:6","Ezra 6:6"]}